  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This proposal introduces a smart contract wallet-based approach for managing NFTs, focusing on utilizing the programmable features of smart contract wallets for NFT asset management. Additionally, it introduces functions such as `nftApprove`, `nftSetApprovalForOneAll`, `nftSetApprovalForAllAll`, `nftGetApproved`, `nftIsApprovedForOneAll`, `nftIsApprovedForAllAll` and `nftTransfer`, which provide enhanced control over NFT transactions. This approach seeks to enhance NFT management by utilizing the built-in features of smart contract wallets, thus offering a more adaptable, secure, and efficient method for managing token transactions.",
